{"tid":1037902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登式微］超過七成青年人認為大灣區有利香港經濟！","createTime":"2019-02-26T09:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T17:03:31.000Z","uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c4a32edd6549647249cdab0c2495ac856f4e250d","tid":1037902,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:20:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有調查發現，超過七成受訪青年人認為粵港澳大灣區有利香港經濟及青年事業發展 ，但只有三成人願意長駐工作。 <br />\n<br />\n青年創研庫上月中在街頭訪問522名18至39歲青年，近四成人認同發展大灣區增加就業機會，六成人願意到大灣區進行工作考察或實習 ，但分別只有五成人願意到大灣區創業及三成人願意長駐工作。<br />\n<br />\n團體認為，大灣區的政策不穩定、商務手續繁複，資訊亦不透明令青年卻步，建議政府設立協調局及為到該處發展的青年提供稅務優惠。"},{"pid":"e539a0e1b3856ad5e863d566563068558c2a0c09","tid":1037902,"uid":20058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:24:01.000Z","msg":"街頭訪問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBias<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccb8d16538438f11499cb60a20ea7707510fbf2","tid":1037902,"uid":107927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"18至39歲青年"},{"pid":"e93b17a2c32fcbed77bee0ec9843683650b9d608","tid":1037902,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>街頭訪問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBias&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲要得500零隻！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9622d305119e7fcc0a376d3fe08ec7b56094eba1","tid":1037902,"uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e93b17a2c32fcbed77bee0ec9843683650b9d608","tid":1037902,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:57:57.000Z"